    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so you won't find a single scratch or speck of dust. It's been kept in a garage and is ready for a new home. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44900.0,
