    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a superlative 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2). This example features the 3.8L flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), delivering a linear 385 hp through a rare 6-speed manual transaxle. The vehicle is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and the Sport Chrono Package, ensuring optimal damping and throttle mapping. Maintenance is current with a documented service history, showing no signs of bore scoring or IMS issues common in earlier iterations. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, and the factory-original Arctic Silver Metallic finish shows consistent micrometer readings. This is a collector-grade specimen with zero mechanical deflection and a pristine undercarriage.",
